{
  "stem": "6719.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, who cares?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said-- but the most significant thing he said was this-- you know what he said?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was not priority.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That tells you the story in a nutshell.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's not a priority.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyhow, I'm going to just get out of a Auschwitz quickly, OK?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we left Auschwitz, uh, when?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In, uh, what, August, 19-- no, not August, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We left Auschwitz in, uh-- in '44, in October.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And uh, after being shuttling around to, again, Buchenwald and Sachsenhausen-- because they couldn't take us in, there weren't enough people-- we ended up in a place called Ohrdruf.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, I, uh-- I have-- I've started to-- the last time we talked, I almost forgot, and then it hit me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "What did they do in Ohrdruf?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They tried to create an underground communication system down there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Now, people in-- in Ohrdruf died-- starvation, hunger, and beatings-- like flies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There were also Russian prisoners.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "For the first time, after all that, because the only Russian prisoners I saw was in the beginning of the war-- of my Auschwitz stay were there, too.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And uh, I became a scribe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, ein schreiber.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I spoke the language.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I could speak.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So they said, can anybody speak German?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Yes, I-- that's the first time in my life I volunteered for anything, but I thought, what the hell, you know, I might as well.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I was like the registrar.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I had to report how many people in the block, how many people died, how many people had to go to the sick bay, and da, da, da, da.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And that was my time down there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we stayed-- as a matter of fact, Ohrdruf was one of the first camps that was liberated in the presence of Eisenhower.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
